Accomplishment Description:
This program is designed to equip ECP Champions with:

1. Effective leadership and decision-making capabilities to guide the implementation of the Expanded Career Progression System;
2. Change management strategies and skills to support smooth transitions, mitigate resistance, and sustain effective implementation of the ECP;
3. Proactive communication and advocacy skills to gain buy-in from teachers, school heads, and other education partners, fostering shared ownership of the ECP

